{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/extras/whatis.png?t=1734361267\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cosmotiles is a relaxing building strategy and puzzle game in which you place colorful blocks on planets. Explore a countless amount of procedurally generated planets, each one offering a unique challenge. Cosmotiles offers a simple game mechanic that allow anyone to create and explore their own planetary wonders. At the same time, Cosmotiles provides enough depth for challenging and rewarding experience for seekers.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1734361267\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cosmotiles has an elegantly simple gameplay. You have to place blocks on planet. Placing a block is rewarded with points based on adjacent tiles when you place them. The more strategically you place your blocks, the more points you score. Once you score enough points, a new planet is unlocked to explore. However, if you run out of tiles to place blocks, the game ends. This is the time when you check your score on the leaderboard and start a new expedition.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/extras/features.png?t=1734361267\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What Cosmotiles offers</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Endless amount of procedurally generated planets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A colorful relaxing and calming experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique mix of strategy and puzzle mechanic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High replay value - every session is different</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strategic placement to beat the highscore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Great for playing now and then</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What Cosmotiles does <strong>not</strong> offer</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4X Strategy   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Trading</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resource Management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combat &amp; Violence</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A cinematic story</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br>The game is inspired from amazing games like ISLANDERS and Dorfromantik. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734361267","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734361267","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/a33db46e7988d764f542a014c76a295e8428e4c4/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734361267","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/a33db46e7988d764f542a014c76a295e8428e4c4/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734361267","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3356760,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3337660/extras/whatis.png?t=1734361267\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cosmotiles is a relaxing building strategy and puzzle game in which you place colorful blocks on planets. Explore a countless amount of procedurally generated planets, each one offering a unique challenge. Cosmotiles offers a simple game mechanic that allow anyone to create and explore their own planetary wonders. At the same time, Cosmotiles provid